                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2413" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0325</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8445 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">埃森克集团内部整合税务之困</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Plight of Internal Integration of ECCIC’s Group’s Tax</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑红霞，郝苓淇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">埃森克科技上海有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海外并购；内部整合；税收筹划；税务风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Overseas mergers and acquisitions; Internal integration; Tax planning; Tax risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着世界经济的全球化，市场竞争日益激烈，企业想要在众多竞争对手中脱颖而出，必须通过创新的商业模式来整合社会资源，以增强企业竞争力。并购这种商业模式成为大多数企业拓展市场之首选。近些年，海外集团并购案也不胜枚举，并购后通过内部整合扩大市场的模式则备受欢迎。内部整合可选方式多、时间长，除了需要从战略角度分析其利弊、在财务方面做好准备外，税收因素也是其实施过程中不可忽视的对象之一，对在并购决策中降低并购成本从而达到预期财务目标起着非常关键的作用。本案例呈现了埃森克集团总部并购曼斯特集团后，对其在中国拥有多个子公司制定内部整合方案中所遇到的一系列税收问题。通过剖析这一案例，可以促进学生理解和掌握并购相关的热点税务问题以及相关税务风险，从而出设计合理可行的并购方案。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the globalization of world economy, market competition is increasingly fierce. Companies aim to stand out of his competitors must integrate social resources through innovative business to enhance enterprise competitiveness. For most enterprises, merger and acquisition of the business model as the first choice of expand market. In recent years, overseas Group deals also abound, after mergers and acquisitions the model by internal integration to expand the market is very popular. Internal integration can be realized through a variety of ways and with a long cycle time, In addition to from a strategic perspective to analyze the advantages and disadvantages, to prepare financially, tax factors is also one of the object can not be ignored in the process of its implementation, which plays a very key role in decrease the cost of mergers and acquisitions in the m&amp;a decision-making and achieve their financial goals. After m&amp;a Mansic Group ,ECCIC Group has a number of subsidiaries and encountered a series of tax problems in setting the company&#39;s internal integration scheme, This case presents these problems. By analyzing the case, students can better to understand and master relevant tax issues of m&amp;a and the related tax risk, and thus design feasible scheme of mergers and acquisitions.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《税收理论与实务》、《税收筹划》、《国际税收》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">税收筹划</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
